# The frontend needs no secrets. AI insights are proxied through the backend
# (POST /api/ai/insight) — the Gemini key lives in the BACKEND environment
# only and must never appear in this public repo or the browser bundle.
#
# API_BASE_URL (optional): backend origin override for the dashboard.
# Default is same-origin (/api + /ws). Only needed when the frontend is
# served from a different host than the backend, e.g. local dev without the
# ng-serve proxy. Inject it as a global before the bundle loads:
#   <script>var API_BASE_URL = "http://localhost:3000";</script>
#API_BASE_URL="http://localhost:3000"
